---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro';
import SiteFooter from '../components/SiteFooter.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Safety Intelligence — predict and prevent risk | SafetyConnect"
  description="Turn safety data into predicted risk, trends, and the insights your safety committee actually uses."
>
  <SiteNav />

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="hero surface-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:56px;align-items:center;">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Safety Intelligence</span>
        <h1 class="display-l" style="margin-bottom:24px;">Where your safety data meets AI.</h1>
        <p class="lead">An AI layer that unifies your safety data and turns it into dashboards, plain-language answers, and proactive flags. The trail your team would have spotted if it had the time, surfaced before the event, not after.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/demo" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Book a 30-minute walkthrough</a>
          <a href="#process" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">See the products it reads</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="product-ui" style="width:100%;">
        <div class="product-ui__chrome">
          <span class="product-ui__dot"></span><span class="product-ui__dot"></span><span class="product-ui__dot"></span>
          <span class="product-ui__url">app.safetyconnect.io / intelligence</span>
        </div>
        <div style="padding:22px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;background:var(--steel-50);">
          <div style="align-self:flex-end;max-width:80%;background:var(--navy);color:#fff;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:14px 14px 4px 14px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.5;">Which of our sites is most likely to have a serious incident this quarter?</div>
          <div style="align-self:flex-start;max-width:88%;background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);padding:14px 16px;border-radius:14px 14px 14px 4px;font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--navy);">
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px;"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l1.6 4.1L18 8.7l-4.4 1.6L12 14l-1.6-3.7L6 8.7l4.4-1.6z"/></svg><span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--steel-600);letter-spacing:0.06em;">SAFETY INTELLIGENCE</span></div>
            Plant 3 stands out. Forklift near-misses in Loading Bay 4 are up 3x this month, two hot-work permits there closed late, and the same crew logged the most fatigue-flagged trips. That combination preceded your last lost-time injury.
            <div style="margin-top:10px;padding:10px;background:rgba(240,80,112,0.07);border-radius:8px;font-size:12.5px;color:var(--navy);"><strong style="color:var(--pink);">Recommended:</strong> hotspot inspection at Loading Bay 4, refresher for the Plant 3 crew, and a permit-discipline review with the shift supervisor.</div>
          </div>
          <div style="align-self:flex-start;display:flex;gap:6px;padding:4px;"><span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--steel-400);"></span><span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--steel-300);"></span><span style="width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--steel-200);"></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What it is -->
<section class="section surface-steel">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">What it is</span>
      <h2 class="display-m">One intelligent layer over all your safety data.</h2>
      <p>Safety Intelligence connects the safety data you already generate, across SafetyConnect and your existing systems, and turns it into clear dashboards, plain-language answers, and early warnings. No new data entry. No waiting on analysts.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(25,167,206,0.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l9 4.9v10.2L12 22 3 17.1V6.9z"/><path d="M12 12l9-4.9M12 12L3 7.1M12 12v10"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px;">All your data, unified</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Modules, sites, and existing systems brought together in one place.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(240,80,112,0.10);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F05070" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px;">Answers in plain language</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Ask a question the way you would ask a colleague, and get an answer.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(26,39,68,0.09);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A2744" stroke-width="1.6" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 3l1.8 4.5L18 9l-4.2 1.5L12 15l-1.8-4.5L6 9l4.2-1.5z"/><path d="M19 14v3M19 20v.01M5 14v3M5 20v.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:8px;">Risk surfaced early</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Patterns and anomalies flagged before they become incidents.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- The problem -->
<section class="section surface-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">The problem</span>
      <h2 class="display-m">Safety data today leaves you blind.</h2>
      <p>The information exists. Getting a clear, timely picture out of it is the hard part.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:20px;max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(240,80,112,0.10);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F05070" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.72-1.71"/><path d="M3 3l18 18" stroke-opacity="0.45"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Disconnected systems</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Safety data sits in separate modules, sites, and spreadsheets that never quite line up.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(25,167,206,0.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6M8 13h8M8 17h5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Manual reporting</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Pulling it together by hand is slow and error-prone, and the report is out of date the moment it lands.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(26,39,68,0.09);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A2744" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 12s3.5-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3.5 7-10 7-10-7-10-7z" stroke-opacity="0.5"/><path d="M3 3l18 18"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Limited visibility</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">No single view of risk across all of your sites, so leadership only sees what makes it into a slide.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:28px;">
        <div style="width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(240,80,112,0.10);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F05070" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 7v5l3.5 2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Late to risk</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Problems surface after the event, when the cost of acting is already at its highest.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- How it works -->
<section class="section surface-steel">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h2 class="display-m">From scattered data to clear answers.</h2>
      <p>Inputs from everywhere your safety data lives, unified by the AI layer, returned as the things your team will actually use.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Flow diagram -->
    <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:14px;padding:40px;margin-bottom:36px;">
      <!-- Inputs row -->
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;margin-bottom:14px;">
        <div style="background:var(--steel-50);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:10px;padding:18px 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(25,167,206,0.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v6c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/><path d="M3 11v6c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3v-6"/></svg></div>
          <div><div style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">SafetyConnect modules</div><div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--steel-700);">Driving, process, observations, incidents, audits, CAPA</div></div>
        </div>
        <div style="background:var(--steel-50);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:10px;padding:18px 22px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;">
          <div style="width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(240,80,112,0.10);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F05070" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg></div>
          <div><div style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Your existing systems</div><div style="font-size:12.5px;color:var(--steel-700);">EHS and enterprise data, via API or upload</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Down arrows -->
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-around;color:var(--steel-400);margin:6px 0 6px;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M6 13l6 6 6-6"/></svg><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M6 13l6 6 6-6"/></svg></div>
      <!-- AI brain -->
      <div style="background:var(--navy);color:#fff;border-radius:12px;padding:20px 28px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:14px;max-width:380px;margin:0 auto;">
        <svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9.5 2a3 3 0 0 0-3 3 3 3 0 0 0-2 5 3 3 0 0 0 1 5 3 3 0 0 0 4 3 3 3 0 0 0 4.5 0 3 3 0 0 0 4-3 3 3 0 0 0 1-5 3 3 0 0 0-2-5 3 3 0 0 0-3-3 3 3 0 0 0-4.5 0z"/></svg>
        <div style="font-size:17px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.01em;">SafetyConnect AI</div>
      </div>
      <!-- Down arrows -->
      <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-around;color:var(--steel-400);margin:6px 0 6px;max-width:560px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M6 13l6 6 6-6"/></svg><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M6 13l6 6 6-6"/></svg><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 5v14M6 13l6 6 6-6"/></svg></div>
      <!-- Outputs row -->
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:16px;">
        <div style="background:rgba(25,167,206,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(25,167,206,0.30);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Unified dashboards</div></div>
        <div style="background:rgba(240,80,112,0.07);border:1px solid rgba(240,80,112,0.30);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Plain-language answers</div></div>
        <div style="background:rgba(26,39,68,0.06);border:1px solid var(--steel-300);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;text-align:center;"><div style="font-size:14px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Proactive flags</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Three steps -->
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;">
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:46px;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal);line-height:1;margin-bottom:10px;">1</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Connect</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Link SafetyConnect and your existing systems, via API or simple data upload.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:46px;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal);line-height:1;margin-bottom:10px;">2</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Unify</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">We bring the data together and keep it current, so the picture is always today’s, not last quarter’s.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:46px;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal);line-height:1;margin-bottom:10px;">3</div>
        <h3 style="font-size:18px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);margin-bottom:6px;">Ask &amp; act</h3>
        <p style="font-size:14.5px;color:var(--steel-700);line-height:1.55;">Question it in plain language, see the flags, and act on what matters. Every action tracked to closure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- What you can ask -->
<section class="section surface-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">In practice</span>
      <h2 class="display-m">Ask it what keeps you up at night.</h2>
      <p>No dashboards to build, no queries to write. Ask the way you would ask a colleague.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:16px;max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;">
      <div style="background:var(--steel-50);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;font-size:15px;color:var(--navy);">“Where are our repeat observations going unclosed?”</div>
      <div style="background:var(--steel-50);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;font-size:15px;color:var(--navy);">“Which drivers are trending towards a serious incident?”</div>
      <div style="background:var(--steel-50);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;font-size:15px;color:var(--navy);">“What changed at the sites with the most near-misses?”</div>
      <div style="background:var(--steel-50);border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 22px;font-size:15px;color:var(--navy);">“Summarise this quarter’s leading indicators for the board.”</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Where it applies -->
<section class="section surface-steel">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header section-header--center">
      <span class="eyebrow">Where it applies</span>
      <h2 class="display-m">Built for the breadth of your safety operation.</h2>
      <p>One view across every domain your safety team owns, and every level of the organisation that needs to see it.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--steel-600);letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;">Across your safety domains</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:16px;margin-bottom:36px;">
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:22px;text-align:center;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(25,167,206,0.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 12px;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 17H3v-5l2-5h11l3 5h2v5h-2"/><circle cx="7.5" cy="17.5" r="2"/><circle cx="17.5" cy="17.5" r="2"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Driving safety</div></div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:22px;text-align:center;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(240,80,112,0.10);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 12px;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#F05070" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 22V10a6 6 0 0 1 12 0v12"/><path d="M6 22H4M18 22h2M9 22v-4M15 22v-4"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Process safety &amp; permits</div></div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:22px;text-align:center;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(26,39,68,0.09);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 12px;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#1A2744" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 22h20L12 2z"/><path d="M12 9v6M12 18v.01"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Incidents &amp; near-misses</div></div>
      <div style="background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--steel-200);border-radius:12px;padding:22px;text-align:center;"><div style="width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:11px;background:rgba(25,167,206,0.12);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 12px;"><svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#19A7CE" stroke-width="1.7" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg></div><div style="font-size:14.5px;font-weight:600;color:var(--navy);">Audits &amp; inspections</div></div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--steel-600);letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:14px;">For everyone who owns safety</div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;">
