    <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-q">Does it work if we only use one product?</summary><div class="faq-a">Yes. It draws on whatever data you have. The more of the platform you use, across driving, process, and forklift safety, plus any existing systems you connect, the richer the cross-product insight becomes.</div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-q">Can it connect to systems outside SafetyConnect?</summary><div class="faq-a">Yes. EHS platforms, ERP, CRM, and asset management data come in via API or simple data upload. We unify them with SafetyConnect data into a single view.</div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-q">Is our data used to train shared models?</summary><div class="faq-a">No. Your data is yours. Safety Intelligence reasons over your own data within your tenant, and is not used to train models for other customers.</div></details>
    <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-q">Can it replace our safety team?</summary><div class="faq-a">No, and it is not meant to. It does the reading and correlating that is beyond human scale, so your team can spend their time on judgement and action rather than trawling through reports.</div></details>
